                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--bc-primary-blue);">Progress Reports</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">Regular updates on development</p>
                <p class="text-sm mt-1" style="color: var(--muted);">See your child's learning journey</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Timmy -->
  <section class="py-20" style="background: transparent;">
    <div class="bc-container">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--bc-primary-blue);">
          Why Parents Love Learning Time with Timmy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">
          The perfect first step in your child's English journey
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8" style="background: var(--glass); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid var(--line); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 140, 69, 0.1), rgba(47, 214, 200, 0.1));">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: var(--bc-success-green);" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--bc-primary-blue);">Natural Language Acquisition</h3>
              <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">
                Children absorb language effortlessly at this age. Our play-based approach mirrors how they learned their first language - naturally and joyfully.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8" style="background: var(--glass); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid var(--line); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 140, 69, 0.1), rgba(47, 214, 200, 0.1));">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: var(--bc-success-green);" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--bc-primary-blue);">Safe & Nurturing Space</h3>
              <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">
                Our teachers create a warm, welcoming environment where every child feels secure to explore, make mistakes, and grow confidently.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8" style="background: var(--glass); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid var(--line); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 140, 69, 0.1), rgba(47, 214, 200, 0.1));">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: var(--bc-success-green);" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
