            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--bc-primary-blue);">Builds School Readiness</h3>
              <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">
                Beyond English, children develop social skills, confidence, and learning habits that prepare them for primary school success.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8" style="background: var(--glass); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid var(--line); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
